productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Moldova and I bought one.
The box this comes in is 5 yard by 6 centimeter and weights 12 kilogram.
I saw one of these in Saint Pierre and Miquelon and I bought one.
My neighbor Albertina has one of these. She works as a gardener and she says it looks humongous.
This paradigm works quite well. It pointedly improves my golf by a lot.
